des:
Use the Hydrogen Stations Alexa skill to find Hydrogen Charging stations in your zip code around the U.S. Simply enable the skill and say "Alexa, open Hydrogen Stations" to begin. 

Or say "Alexa, ask Hydrogen Stations..."
• get me zip code 91765 
• Is there charging station around 92675

This is a beta version which only holds information on basic Hydrogen Charging Stations for now. Stay tuned, more features will be added soon!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
